item.title: CVE-2017-7736|2024-09-16T17:28:23.537Z -- fortinet%2C%20inc. -- fortinet%20fortiweb
item.description: A stored Cross-site Scripting (XSS) vulnerability in Fortinet FortiWeb webUI Certificate View page in 5.8.0, 5.7.1 and earlier, allows attackers to inject arbitrary web script or HTML via special crafted malicious certificate import.
